verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
NOT BY MIGHT, NOR BY POWER,
But by My Spirit, saith the Lord. Not by might, nor
by power, but by My Spirit, saith the Lord. These
mountains shall be removed, these mountains
shall be removed, these mountains shall be
removed, by My Spirit, saith the Lord.
